ComicInfo.Title: High Stakes Part 3
ComicInfo.Series: G.I. Joe: A Real American Hero
ComicInfo.Summary: High Stakes Part 3: As Cobra opens the doors of their Cobra Casino to the public, G.I. Joe sends a team undercover to explore the casino. As Agent Helix and Dawn explore behind the wings one of the new B.A.T. models is sent to kill them.
